<body>
<b>Mouse with scroll wheel:</b>
<table border=0>
<tr valign=top><td>Pan:</td><td><ul><li>Left mouse button click & drag - all directions<li>Left mouse button click once to center view</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Zoom:</td><td><ul><li>Use the scroll wheel on the mouse<li>Left & Right mouse (both buttons) click & drag - up and down<li>Left mouse button double click to zoom and center</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Tilt:</td><td><ul><li>Right mouse button click & drag - up and down<li>"Page Up" and "Page Down" on the keyboard</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Rotate:</td><td><ul><li>Right mouse button click & drag - left and right</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Stop:</td><td><ul><li>Spacebar</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Reset heading:</td><td><ul><li>N</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Reset all:</td><td><ul><li>R</ul></td></tr>
</table>
<br>
<b>Single button mouse:</b>
<table border=0>
<tr valign=top><td>Pan:</td><td><ul><li>Left mouse button click & drag - all directions<li>Left mouse button click once to center view</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Zoom:</td><td><ul><li>Hold "Ctrl" on the keyboard and Left mouse button click & drag - up and down<li>Left mouse button double click to zoom and center</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Tilt:</td><td><ul><li>Hold "Shift" on the keyboard and Left mouse button click & drag - up and down<li>"Page Up" and "Page Down" on the keyboard</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Rotate:</td><td><ul><li>Hold "Shift" on the keyboard and Left mouse button click & drag - left and right</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Stop:</td><td><ul><li>Spacebar</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Reset heading:</td><td><ul><li>N</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Reset all:</td><td><ul><li>R</ul></td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
